 
Global Tumor-on-a-chip Market Insights
Tumor-on-a-chip Market size was valued at USD 0.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 16.7% from 2024 to 2030.

Tumor-on-a-Chip Market Overview
The Tumor-on-a-Chip market is projected to reach USD 54 million by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 30.8% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by technological advancements, increasing demand for personalized medicine, and the need for more reliable preclinical models. The market is segmented into product types, applications, end-users, and regions, each contributing uniquely to its expansion. Source

